          "description": "First time meeting with the office, its a cool place, great music, art work etc. Not a stuffy place and in a great location should want to go do some shopping or have a great meal after you get your teeth tuned up and looking and feeling good.\nDr lee is very approachable and a seems like great guy an avid music lover so the vibe was top shelf.\nI am considering veneers and I saw him on IG and wanted to get to know the office first and I will say that I felt really good and walk away knowing I would be back.\nYou wont be dissapointed, I m very particular at my age and the place is the real deal.\nCheers TJB",
