          "contributor_id": "109914475603202045970",
          "user_review_count": 2,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaTXWa185kfbaql_XyEuf_RUPuD6xv_SPu6lURCCKmQ3fTsFs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I\u2019m really delayed writing this review, we\u2019ve been traveling so much. I went to Smile dental in January and had a wonderful experience. I started the process of a root canal and everything went incredibly well. Being a couple of months post procedure, I\u2019m still pretty comfortable. My husband and the owner were even able to connect over Opera, as my husband is a producer. We live in SEAsia so it\u2019s really important to us that I get back to Smile dental  to complete the process but overall, I loved my initial visit. The staff made it even more enjoyable as everyone was so welcoming. I would highly recommend this dental office to anyone in the NYC area. If we resided in NYC, this would certainly be our permanent, long term dental care team.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tjelFVbEJZVGxVWVMxMVlWaDNTV2N4WTJOd1UyYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x5952a09fe294b236!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkczQUlBYTlUYS11YVh3SWcxY2NwU2c%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "2 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-04-05T04:32:50+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Marc Keller",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "115712266814882484327",
          "user_review_count": 5,
          "user_photo_count": 7,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPfgs6B3Ml_ENVGa9KNykfBywc5BPaqBySYKrx0AH9zpm4qv_j=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Dr. Gause and team \u2014 thank you for an outstanding year of care.\n\nOver the past year, I\u2019ve worked with your office through an implant, whitening, and Invisalign teeth straightening, and the experience has been exceptional from start to almost finished. The entire staff is professional, friendly, and truly best-in-class.\n\nEvery visit felt like walking into a polished, professional environment with a warm welcome. I was always greeted with engaging conversation (and even offered a bottle of water), the wait times were consistently short, and I never once felt rushed during any appointment. Dr. Gause and the team took the time to explain each step clearly and made the whole process comfortable and confidence-boosting.\n\nIf you\u2019re considering implant work, whitening, or Invisalign, I couldn\u2019t recommend Dr. Gause and his team more highly.\n\nThank you to the entire team!\n\nBest,\nMarc Keller\n\nPs. Will follow up with phots next month. :)",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWbVRXVkRiWEZSUW5WU2JtSmtZbE5SWmxwUVNFRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x5952a09fe294b236!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkVmTWVDbXFRQnVSbmJkYlNRZlpQSEE%7C%7C?hl=en",
