          "description": "Smile Design Manhattan is amazing!!!!! Rachel at the front is friendly and lovely. Dr. Meyers is the sweetest and so happy I met her. Samantha was so caring, knowledgeable, fun and patient and a beacon of professionalism. Everyone in the office is so nice and I am starting my Invisalign journey with them and I can\u2019t wait to post before and after photos!",
