          "description": "Dr. Gause has an absolutely wonderful, comforting approach. His vast knowledge and expertise is apparent as he discussed with me his recommendations based on his findings and my desires. It was easy to settle in with the staff who were pleasant, kind and professional and most of all concerned with my comfort.",
