          "description": "It was a relief to meet Dr. Meyers. Her feather-light touch, patient/reassuring approach, and whip-smart efficiency combine into perfect results, and (I can't believe I'm saying this) an enjoyable experience at the dentist. Everyone at Smile Design is excellent--Dr. Meyers, Dr. G, Dr. Copeland, and the hygienists and assistants make a great team.",
