          "description": "While it's fair to say that none of us relish a visit to any dentist, Smile Designs makes the task of keeping your mouth healthy -- and your smile brilliant -- an enjoyable experience (I never thought I'd say this about any dentist!). Quality of care is unmatched, facilities are state-of-art, and communication is timely, friendly, clear, personalized and supportive. I highly recommend! Also, art lovers will relish the fact that the dental offices double as art gallery. Very cool place to have important dental work done with a plan that works for you. (This is not a paid endorsement, BTW - just notes from my experience).",
